

1. Burn several different ideal flavors of bsd.
2. Get yourself a decent dvd setup for writing to the OS. This thing could take time.
3. Print and read the handbook. It is gospel for surviving BSD.
4. pray to God and confirm your BIOS settings. Expect you may go there several times.
5. Have a reliable disk as you could fail SSD banks just trying to get the thing to work.
6. Welcome to true distro!!
